{
  "stem": "3658.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So of course they knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the Allies were bombing, was air raids, we were put on a field so that they can see us, you know?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they were bombing, in the daytime, all everybody, all the ones from the camps, we had to get out and on a-- sort of on a big area so that the bombers, the people that were bombing, could see that.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That they wouldn't bomb that area.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, that's what happened with Gusen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then we all assembled.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were marching us to Gunskirchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's the last camp where I went to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was the death march.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because there we marched for days from Gusen, from everywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were only, only Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was this guy with me that we kept together in the camps.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And his name is Braham Stern that lives here in Sydney.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- he couldn't walk anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I begged him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, come.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to come because they'll kill you here, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If we are all gone, and they find that-- Left?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and you knew because the Jews had a special marking, you know-- yellow, the yellow mark.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, you've got to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You've got to come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I lifted him up, begging him to come.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've had it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't move anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just leave me alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I left him there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And years later, I found him in Sydney.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he was liberated before me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So anyway, then they took us on this march which is really was a death march.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were deliberately shooting us from front, from the back, from every other-- so that there'd be less people.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
